  "_comment": "Copy this file to adobe_sign_config.json. Fill in client_id/client_secret/redirect_uri from your Acrobat Sign Application (Account > Acrobat Sign API > API Applications > Configure OAuth). Never share adobe_sign_config.json or paste its contents into chat -- refresh_token grants ongoing API access to your account. authorize_host/token_host only need changing if adobe_sign.py's defaults (na1 shard) don't match your account.",
